channel.title: [Added] Create Org. Identifier XI-IATI-CWSEC For The Commonwealth Secretariat
channel.description:
The Commonwealth Secretariat require the following information to be added on their behalf to the IATI Organisation Identifier Codelist at http://iatistandard.org/201/codelists/IATIOrganisationIdentifier/1
Code: XI-IATI-CWSEC
Name: The Commonwealth Secretariat
Description: The Commonwealth is a voluntary association of 52 independent and equal sovereign states . Its guiding principles are contained in the [Commonwealth Charter](http://thecommonwealth.org/node/1914)
URL:http://thecommonwealth.org/
